# ============================================================
# Movie Platform API - Test Suite
# Requirements: REST Client extension (Huachao Mao) in VSCode
# Make sure the server is running: docker compose up -d
# ============================================================


# ── HEALTH ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health


# ── MONGODB: MOVIES ──────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all movies (sorted by rating)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies

###

### Filter movies by genre
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies?genre=Sci-Fi

###

### Get a single movie with full details
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies/mov_inception

###

### Get a single movie with Neo4j recommendations (pass user for social recs)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies/mov_inception?user_id=usr_001


# ── MONGODB: ATLAS SEARCH ────────────────────────────────────

### Search movies by plot keyword (fuzzy - typos allowed)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies/search?q=dream

###

### Search by director name
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies/search?q=nolan

###

### Search with a typo (fuzzy matching)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies/search?q=matix


# ── MONGODB: REVIEWS ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all reviews for a movie
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies/mov_inception/reviews

###

### Add a new review
POST http://localhost:3000/api/movies/mov_dune/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "usr_003",
  "rating": 5,
  "text": "Epic world-building, Villeneuve at his best!"
}


# ── MONGODB: USERS ───────────────────────────────────────────

### Get a user profile (includes Neo4j follows)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/usr_001

###

### Get all reviews written by a user
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/usr_001/reviews


# ── MONGODB: DASHBOARD (Aggregation Pipelines) ───────────────

### Pipeline 1 - Genre statistics (movie count + avg rating per genre)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/dashboard?type=genre_stats

###

### Pipeline 2 - Top 10 movies leaderboard
GET http://localhost:3000/api/dashboard

###

### Hit dashboard again - should return from_cache: true (Redis cache)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/dashboard


# ── REDIS: TRENDING ──────────────────────────────────────────

### Get trending movies (from Redis sorted set leaderboard)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trending

###

### Increment a movie's trending score (simulates a view)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/trending/mov_inception/view

###

### Trending again - Inception score should now be 1 higher
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trending


# ── REDIS: SESSION ───────────────────────────────────────────

### Request with a valid session token (seeded by seed-redis.js)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/usr_991
Authorization: Bearer session:usr_991_token

###

### Request with an invalid/expired session token
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/usr_001
Authorization: Bearer session:fake_token
